title: It's Always Sunny in Philadelphia
fullTitle: It's Always Sunny in Philadelphia (TV Series 2005â€“ )

episodes.title: The Gang Exploits the Mortgage Crisis
episodes.plot: While Frank buys a foreclosed house with intentions of selling it for profit, Mac and Dennis become hot-headed real estate brokers, and Dee takes advantage of a suburban couple looking to hire a surrogate mother.

episodes.title: The Gang Hits the Road
episodes.plot: The gang takes Dee's new subcompact car and a U-haul on the road with the intentions of hitting the Grand Canyon, and Charlie attempts to expand his horizons.

episodes.title: The Great Recession
episodes.plot: Mac and Dennis try to cut back Paddy's expenses by firing Dee and Charlie, and Frank figures out a clever way to keep the bar afloat.

episodes.title: The Gang Gives Frank an Intervention
episodes.plot: After Frank embarrasses himself at the funeral of a deceased relative, Dennis and Dee decide that it's finally time to give him an intervention for his reckless lifestyle.

episodes.title: The Waitress Is Getting Married
episodes.plot: Dee discovers that the waitress Charlie is obsessed with is getting married to her ex-boyfriend and plots to derail the wedding, while Mac, Frank and Dennis try to get Charlie back on the dating scene.

episodes.title: The World Series Defense
episodes.plot: Fighting a series of traffic tickets, Dennis, along with the rest of the gang, tell the judge about their horrific experiences at Game 5 of the Phillies' world series.

episodes.title: The Gang Wrestles for the Troops
episodes.plot: The gang decides to put on a wrestling show for troops returning home while Dee courts a soldier who doesn't seem like the person she's chatting online with.

episodes.title: Paddy's Pub: Home of the Original Kitten Mittens
episodes.plot: The gang attempts to create a merchandising angle for Paddy's when a convention comes to Philly.

episodes.title: Mac and Dennis Break Up
episodes.plot: Taking Dee's advice seriously, Mac and Dennis decide that they're too co-dependent on each other and need to spend time apart. Meanwhile Charlie and Frank help Dee out with a major cat problem in her apartment.

episodes.title: The D.E.N.N.I.S. System
episodes.plot: Dennis presents his fool-proof plan for picking up chicks, but soon finds that the gang each has their own fool-proof plans for one-upping each other.

episodes.title: Mac and Charlie Write a Movie
episodes.plot: After Dee gets cast as an extra in the new M. Night Shyamalan movie, Mac and Charlie see a perfect opportunity to pitch their script, while Frank becomes a casting agent for Dennis.

episodes.title: The Gang Reignites the Rivalry
episodes.plot: Mac, Dennis, and Charlie seek revenge on another bar after their 10-year ban in a local flip-cup tournament is lifted, but find they need serious practice. Dee discovers new skills, and Frank wears tight pants.
